Package: ep2b
Title: Import and Examine Excel Documents Simply 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Michael", "Littrell", email = "mlittrell@tntech.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Reads all sheets from an Excel workbook into a named list of
    tibbles and prints a summary of each sheet's dimensions, column types,
    and basic statistics. Designed to shorten the initial "what's in this
    file?" step of exploratory analysis.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Imports:
    readxl,
    tibble,
    cli,
    purrr,
    dplyr
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
